      "text": [
        "هَا أَ يُتِمُّ أَوْ يُقَصِّرُ قَالَ «يُتِمُّ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1280 - Abd al-Rahman bin al-Hajjaj asked Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) about a man who owns lands that are close to one another and he travels between them. Should he complete his prayers or shorten them?\nImam (as) replied: \"He should complete [his prayers].\""
        ]
      }
    },
